    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Timber, steel, or precast concrete columns serving as subsurface supports for vertical loads; distinct from "piers (foundation components)" which are larger and are never clustered.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
